{"tid":1960756,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老第一滴血，葵盛東邨六男疑聚賭收告票","createTime":"2020-04-06T10:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T05:34:10.000Z","uid":23833,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c7105f917effeac0cd8a3bb4e11d43b2ee25bb62","tid":1960756,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:50:50.000Z","msg":"政府一周前開始實施「限聚令」，截至4月4日凌晨零時，共巡查政府管轄的公眾地方合共7060次，警方及各部門合共作出882次口頭勸喻，惟未有作出任何檢控。據了解，葵青警區昨日向六名男子各發出2000元定額罰款告票。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，警方接到市民報案，指有一批人在葵盛東邨盛興樓地下聚集，懷疑在下棋聚賭，違反「限聚令」。警方到場後，發現有6名男子在上址下棋，並上前作出勸喻，要求他們保持一定距離或離開，不過6名男子未有理會警方勸喻，警方隨即向6名年齡介乎52至68歲的男子發出告票。<br />\n<br />\n政府於上月28日刊登憲報，訂立《預防及控制疾病（禁止羣組聚集）規例》（《規例》）（第599G章），禁止於公眾地方進行多於4人的羣組聚集會，為期14天至4月11日。違例者最高可被判處罰款25000元及監禁6個月。參加受禁羣組聚集的人，可藉繳付定額罰款2000元，解除因該罪行而須負的法律責任。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1741098\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1741098&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLbzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=634569b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1741098</a>"},{"pid":"2a7913f39d418184e3af369cb424f388546631a4","tid":1960756,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01705029a2c195426ee8e6014b04d3c8e31703a","tid":1960756,"uid":39268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"未贏已經要交2k<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81c222c645ee73963b3f838fbec18e77e9eb13f","tid":1960756,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:53:36.000Z","ms